{"tid":1902658,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文] 拎藍絲維穩費救手足","createTime":"2020-02-28T12:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T15:52:11.000Z","uid":247129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e76ca074b1953c83ea3bdbcecf78058f89d56f0","tid":1902658,"uid":247129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T12:52:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢排冇得出街，睇多左電視，成日見到個好核突既廣告話登記左就有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">500萬</span></span>酬金，本著FC精神，我決定查下個廣告係做乜9（利申，非打手）<br />\n<br />\n先查下咩叫千萬求一路，原來就係好耐之前賣哂報紙頭版個單<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">維穩野</span></span>，個時以為只係會吸引班腦殘<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍絲</span>參加，但我睇睇下佢個遊戲規則，發覺原來係可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">拎佢d錢黎救手足</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點拎佢d錢<br />\n1. 之前個d初賽已經完左，所以可以唔9理佢，而家去到 final 十強<br />\n2. 十強中投票選4個，投票都有錢分，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">好似買馬咁，四重彩</span></span>，最後中左會有獎金，佢話有500萬<br />\n<br />\n我睇左個十強，同d fd講先知原來入面有d都係黃絲手足，我覺得佢係黃既方案係 78, 37, 4, 18。呢十強最後贏第一個位有100萬獎金，第二三四都有幾十萬。我再利申，我真係以為只係會吸引班腦殘藍絲，但而家睇返呢幾個入到十強既手足，係可以入去<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拎藍絲嘅資源</span></span>，我<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對唔住，誤會左你地</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我心諗，咁不如集合晒手足嘅力量，拎晒啲錢，仲可以幫埋入邊d手足去贏，就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">好似蛇齋餅糉</span></span>咁，羅哂佢d資源，再<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一票不投民賤聯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢到14號就截止，由於事態緊急，我直接喺呢一度開Post，有唔岩既，多多得罪<br />\n<br />\n票投比手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ideasforhk.org/#/r\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ideasforhk.org%2F%23%2Fr&d=2%2B%2BG2pXT7lWIneVuf1o%2BJOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=0728504e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ideasforhk.org/#/r</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J5m5mCE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ5m5mCE.jpg&h=91dd31bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4f4073e306f8b03ed08214c779708a66e52a593","tid":1902658,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"大概睇咗幾條片<br />\n包括你講嗰幾個號碼<br />\n完全唔覺得有邊個係黃喎<br />\n參加者又冇話會拎啲錢點樣幫手捉<br />\n個page一註冊就問我攞個人資料<br />\nerrrr<br />\n唔係唔想幫<br />\n但需要更多evidence <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccad591a60350b180ed76a9e7349aaf73ad383fc","tid":1902658,"uid":247129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4f4073e306f8b03ed08214c779708a66e52a593","tid":1902658,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T13:06:24.000Z","msg":"大概睇咗幾條片<br />\n包括你講嗰幾個號碼<br />\n完全唔覺得有邊個係黃喎<br />\n參加者又冇話會拎啲錢點樣幫手捉<br />\n個page一註冊就問我攞個人資料<br />\nerrrr<br />\n唔係唔想幫<br />\n但需要更多evidence <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:06:20.000Z","msg":"我個fd同其中夫婦個對參賽者好熟，佢地係開補習社，雖然之前為左啲學生冇罷工罷市，但佢地嘅員工請假，一律不扣假不扣糧。<br />\n同埋佢地參賽者之間都有交流（互片），黃嘅當然唔會想藍嘅贏啦，好壁壘分明"},{"pid":"26a0a97436bd3c90535ac1d9ee876a889a16f6bf","tid":1902658,"uid":161274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:09:43.000Z","msg":"冇FC有d危險<br />\n唔想咁樣交個人資料"},{"pid":"5e3bba24ea2aae5a89cbb352f69f97171d501439","tid":1902658,"uid":247129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26a0a97436bd3c90535ac1d9ee876a889a16f6bf","tid":1902658,"uid":161274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:09:43.000Z","msg":"冇FC有d危險<br />\n唔想咁樣交個人資料"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T15:47:01.000Z","msg":"我都諗左陣，但淨係電話號碼，又唔洗名唔洗身分證，收到 cold call 亂打個機會仲大"},{"pid":"c5049f8a78e9f6e55c76e57dcf4f7842b73a74f6","tid":1902658,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20